### ABIS API sample requests (VS Code REST Client / JetBrains HTTP client)
### Run the API first:  dotnet run --project src/ABIS.Api

@host = http://localhost:5199
@apiKey = dev-local-key

### Service info (anonymous)
GET {{host}}/

### Health — liveness (anonymous)
GET {{host}}/health

### Health — readiness: DB reachable (anonymous; 503 if not)
GET {{host}}/health/ready

### List jobs (auth required)
GET {{host}}/api/jobs?pageSize=5
X-Api-Key: {{apiKey}}

### List jobs sorted by status (desc) — allowlisted sort/dir
GET {{host}}/api/jobs?sort=jobStatus&dir=desc
X-Api-Key: {{apiKey}}

### Unknown sort field -> 400 (lists allowed fields)
GET {{host}}/api/jobs?sort=bogus
X-Api-Key: {{apiKey}}

### QA test results: filter by position + date range, newest first
GET {{host}}/api/test-results?position=T&from=2026-01-01&to=2026-12-31
X-Api-Key: {{apiKey}}

### One job
GET {{host}}/api/jobs/1001
X-Api-Key: {{apiKey}}

### Coils processed by a job
GET {{host}}/api/jobs/1001/coils
X-Api-Key: {{apiKey}}

### Create a coil on receipt
POST {{host}}/api/coils
X-Api-Key: {{apiKey}}
Content-Type: application/json

{ "coilAlloy2": "6061", "coilTemper": "T6", "coilGauge": 0.25, "coilWidth": 48.5, "netWt": 15000, "coilStatus": 1 }

### Update a coil (move / status)
PATCH {{host}}/api/coils/5001
X-Api-Key: {{apiKey}}
Content-Type: application/json

{ "coilLocation": "DOCK-7", "coilStatus": 2 }

### Create a customer
POST {{host}}/api/customers
X-Api-Key: {{apiKey}}
Content-Type: application/json

{ "customerName": "DELTA EXTRUSIONS", "customerShortName": "DELTA" }

### Audit log (newest first)
GET {{host}}/api/audit-log?pageSize=10
X-Api-Key: {{apiKey}}

### Missing key -> 401
GET {{host}}/api/jobs
